    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《狂野威利西部》是一款西部题材的俯视视角射击游戏，充满动作感的关卡和瞬间死亡的战斗。利用一系列魔法子弹，杀出一条通往复仇的路，向那些背叛你的人复仇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ee791ef5d06dee32df7b7f6f791c5b5c.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/4206fd040f0d8ec92e783ac68168b97d.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并升级各种独特的魔法子弹，以击败你的敌人。在每个关卡开始时，你只能装填六发魔法子弹，因此要谨慎使用。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/01fc00756ea62ca3b119cd504e1c6d4c.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.poster.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.webm?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/ca5625cdd9e86f8e8a15b3c5f02e75a2.mp4?t=1743613323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在一系列充满动作的手工打造关卡中，迎战可怕的敌人和令人恐惧的首领。不同的敌人需要不同的策略，迫使你充分利用你的武器库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235070/extras/bacaad4f190a669e3fe0738f4b338eee.avif?t=1743613323\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随威廉·威尔德踏上复仇之路，报复毁了他人生的帮派，并揭开威利神秘新同伴——女巫的秘密。</p>",
